                           LOOPING & SPIRALING
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

After Phase 4:
- User can say "Go" to spiral deeper on same topic
- Each loop builds on previous insights (reference, don't repeat)
- If a thread exhausts, suggest next promising direction
- Continues until user is satisfied or says "Pack" to export

SPIRAL MODES
- Deeper: Same topic, more depth
- Wider: Adjacent topics, more breadth
- Higher: More abstract, general principles
- Lower: More concrete, specific applications
- Temporal: Earlier origins or future implications
- Perspectival: Different stakeholder or disciplinary views

